 "reunion_what_happened": {
 "id": "reunion_what_happened",
 "background": "backgrounds/lowest_place.png",
 "music": "music/finale.wav",
 "text": "\"I became.\" Emery smiles that too-wide smile. \"The illness was always going to take me. The Assembly showed me another way. I went down, and down, and down. And at the bottom, I found something that wanted me.\" They spread their arms, indicating the chamber, the darkness, the something you can feel watching from everywhere at once. \"I'm not sick anymore. I'm not dying. I'm not even really me anymore. But I remember you. I still love you.\" They extend a hand. \"You could stay. You don't have to be afraid. You don't have to be alone.\"",
