 "music": "music/finale.wav",
 "text": "Emery laughs. It's almost a human sound. Almost. \"Home? This is home now. More than that house ever was.\" They step closer. You can smell them now, earth and something sweeter, something organic and alive. \"The illness was going to take everything. The pain, the exhaustion, the slow vanishing of who I used to be. This was better. This is better.\" They reach for your hand. Their skin is cold but somehow also warm. Wrong temperature. Impossible temperature. \"You could stay. With me. Forever.\"",
